snippet.title: Real World Interviews Qs: How to Implement Linked List?
snippet.description:
Real world interviews almost always involve implementing or at the very least discussing how a linked list implements insertion and deletion of objects.  Today's lesson will dive into a couple of different techniques on how these functions can be written out.  I hope you're able to knock out these problems if you're ever asked in an interview.
